headline: GE Vernova Stock: Is GEV Outperforming the Industrials Sector?
summary: Though GE Vernova has outperformed the industrial sector over the past year, Wall Street analysts maintain a cautiously optimistic outlook on the stock’s prospects.

headline: QuesTek Innovations Develops New Printable Alloy Concept with Support from Aerospace and Energy Leaders
summary: QuesTek Innovations, a leader in computational materials engineering is working with a global leader in niobium production to develop a high-temperature alloy design concept optimized for additive manufacturing. The effort aims to support the development of next-generation alloys for the aerospace and energy industries, with a focus on scalability, supply chain resilience, and application-specific performance. The concept is being shaped with input from respected industry leaders — including GE
